## 🎭 Role Adopted: ⚡ Performance Engineer

### Focus areas
- DOM rendering: reduce layout thrash; use fragments; cache selectors
- Timers: avoid duplicated intervals; pause when appropriate
- Dashboard polling: keep it non-intrusive and avoid redundant full refresh loops
- Network: minimize payloads; handle failures gracefully without blocking UX
